<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Game of Life</title>
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #121212;
          color: white;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 10px;
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 800px;
          overflow-y: auto; /* Rende il contenuto scorrevole */
          height: 80vh; /* Imposta un'altezza fissa per il container */
      }
      h1 {
          font-size: 3rem;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .rules-list {
          list-style: none;
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
      }
      .rules-list li {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
          text-align: left;
      }
      .rule-number {
          font-weight: bold;
          color: #ff6600;
      }
      ul.rules-list {
          text-align: left;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding-left: 20px;
          max-width: 500px;
      }
      p strong {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          color: #ff6600;
      }
      .btn {
          background: #ff6600;
          color: white;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          transition: 0.3s;
          display: inline-block;
          margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
          background: #cc5200;
      }
      .btn-back {
          background-color: #444;
      }
      /* Stile per il form */
      .game-form .form-group {
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .game-form .form-label {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          color: #ff6600;
          text-align: center;
          display: block;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .game-form .form-control {
          width: 60%;
          padding: 10px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          border: 1px solid #ccc;
          background-color: #1e1e1e;
          color: white;
          font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .game-form .form-control:focus {
          border-color: #ff6600;
          outline: none;
      }
      .game-form .btn-primary {
          background-color: #ff6600;
          color: white;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          transition: 0.3s;
          display: inline-block;
          margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .game-form .btn-primary:hover {
          background-color: #cc5200;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Sei pronto?</h1>
  <p>Mettiti comodo e goditi la generazione del Gioco della Vita secondo le tue regole.</p>


  <%= button_to 'Avvia la generazione', '#', method: :post, class: 'btn' %>
</div>
<%= button_to 'Logout', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: 'btn' %>
<p><a href="<%= root_path %>" class="btn btn-back">Torna alla Home</a></p>
</body>
</html>
